name: • Is the sea infinite or is my vision too short? •
description: The sea is the world, or was it the other way around? Well, in the end it all boils down to a lake of ideas, opportunities, thoughts, and more...  The world is too big to have only one sunrise, or only one way, or only one path. The great mystery of life doesn't change, why am I here? but there has to be a why?
